                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-90-off529 t18261207-90-cd530"></join>, 5 half-crowns, the monies of 
                     <persName id="t18261207-90-victim606" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
